ProMED
<promed@promedmail.org>
[It is most unusual to find DHF occurring only one year after the first
reports of dengue in a country. The 1977 outbreak was dengue type 1. Can
anyone tell us what type the 1978 epidemic was, & the age group of the fatal
cases? Perhaps these were the rare type of DHF not due to sequential
infection by 2 different dengue types.
ProMED has in the past received donations from GIDEON, which is an
encyclopedic, searchable database on infectious diseases & their treatment.
It can be downloaded free from http://www.cyinfo.com - Mod.JW
...........................................jw

